{"tid":1944903,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Dyson 僅用 10 天設計了全新呼吸機 CoVent　英國政府立即下單訂 1 萬台","createTime":"2020-03-26T16:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T17:58:56.000Z","uid":104138,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5fa1d291294a030bd732e165cd202081575754cd","tid":1944903,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:59:47.000Z","msg":"英國疫情嚴峻，而當中最缺乏的物資就是呼吸機，而為了協助 NHS 抗疫，由下周起 Dyson 及空中巴士 Airbus 將會開始生產呼吸機，預計生產 3 萬部。由於 NHS 希望將呼吸機數目增至 3 萬部，英國首相找 Dyson 公司始創人「發明家」 James Dyson 幫忙，最後他跟工程師僅花了 10 天便完成全新呼吸機 CoVent 的設計，而英國政府也立即下單訂 1 萬台。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/covent.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2Fcovent.jpg&h=02dc0848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次 Dyson 跟 TTP 公司合作，新的呼吸機安全、有效、易於移動，當中使用了 Dyson 空氣清新機的技術及使用數碼摩打。 James Dyson 表示最大的挑戰在用極短時間完成設計及量產。而 Dyson 正等待監管機構的批准，除了為英國生產外，Dyson 亦有意在國際推出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/03/26/dyson-covent/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2020%2F03%2F26%2Fdyson-covent%2F&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWRz2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=291d0d2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/03/26/dyson-covent/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/241379/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/241379/page/1</a><br />\n連登仔: 除左user friendly 同輕巧d 都冇咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0259fc131ff34deb0ada5d08a4f1270e375db251","tid":1944903,"uid":140538,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T17:00:55.000Z","msg":"有咩需要加最尾嗰句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />覺得自己好好笑?"},{"pid":"3776c54b206db8847f67fd9db17cacf3b0183d05","tid":1944903,"uid":57914,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0259fc131ff34deb0ada5d08a4f1270e375db251